---
description: Utility library conventions
globs: src/lib/**/*.ts
---

- Pure functions, no React dependencies
- Export individual functions, not classes
- `units.ts`: mm is canonical; convert at boundaries
- `svg.ts`: Sanitize with DOMPurify; limited element subset
- `pdf.ts`: Use pdf-lib; dimensions in points (72/inch)
- `patterns.ts`: Validate with Zod schemas
